  "privacySectionYourRights": "۴۔ آپ کے حقوق",
  "privacyRightsBody": "You have the following rights regarding your data: • Access: View تمام your personal and صحت data within the app or request a data eبرآمد • Correction: ترمیم your پروفائل information at any وقت through ترمیم Pپروفائل • Deletion: Request account deletion through ترتیبات > Data & رازداری > حذف کریں Account. • Restriction: Limit how certain data is processed by adjusting your notification and sharing preferences. • Objection: Object to specific data processing activities by contacting our Data Protection Officer. • Withdrawal of Consent: You may withdraw consent at any وقت without affecting the lawfulness of prior processing. To exercise any of these rights, contact us at privacy@vitalseker.com or through the in-app معاونت feature.",
